# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Allowed types: feat, fix, refactor, chore, docs, test, ci, build, perf
# Scope: module / package name, e.g. api, model, tool, middleware, hooks, sandbox
# Subject: under 72 chars, imperative mood, no trailing period
#
# Body (optional, wrap at 72): why this change, not what.
# Reference issues with: Refs #123, Fixes #456.
#
# Breaking change marker:
# BREAKING CHANGE: describe the incompatible public API change.
#
# Agent co-authorship:
# Co-authored-by: Agent Name <agent@example.org>
